-MAlJfiaQa5kJeHCyOIvLSw">Thu lô - 秋爐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91-trung-t%C3%ACnh-T%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-gi%E1%BA%A3/poem-Hg-7eOvtAxpY8-66f5D-4Q">Tố trung tình - Tụng điếu giả - 訴衷情－頌釣者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4-S%E1%BB%9F-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-ki%C3%AAm-m%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-VusrYuqrkvq24lkjJ2HUYQ">Tương thích Ngô Sở, lưu biệt Chương sứ quân lưu hậu kiêm mạc phủ chư công, đắc liễu tự - 將適吳楚，留別章使君留後兼幕府諸公，得柳字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-C%C6%A1/%E1%BB%A8c-T%E1%BA%A7n-Nga/poem-slNTlztlhEJINjf7ds5Fkg">Ức Tần Nga - 憶秦娥</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-C%C6%A1/author-pFXALvgx6W3AfbutIRgwXA">Hoàng Cơ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
